{
  "stem": "1292.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember just falling down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At that stage, I gave up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that stage, it was my lowest point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And even then, suddenly, to my biggest surprise, I heard noises.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Appell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Appell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Appell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was amazed that I am still alive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That, I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We have been called out for the appell.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We stand in this rain and cold-- terrible day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was very bad weather.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then, they put us into diffident barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, it was three-story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very close, we did sleep.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There wasn't much of the blankets or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there, it was terrible hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Terrible hunger.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called a coffee, which was like brown water, in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then what they called a soup-- it was just like another water, you know-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember I didn't eat four days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was what you not call eating, yes?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we was called in the appell, or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really think I must have been sort of semi-conscious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I did see, next to the barrack, must have been some sort of kitchen or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did see a cart of cabbages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did risk my life to just run and grab a cabbage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember this bit of cabbage, so nobody would see me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And to my amazement, I digested raw cabbage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, it was another very terrible time when I was terribly hungry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was in the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my friend, who did sleep next to me, she did find out that our friend-- I knew her too, her name was Felka Pleshovska, that she is working somewhere as a nurse close to Mengele, must have been, right?",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
